high_descs: move  right to the bed
pick up the phone from the bed
turn right and head towards the table
place the phone in the drawer
locate the top of the drawer
pick up the phone on the drawer
move the the drawer
place the phone inside the drawer
anns.task_desc: place two phones inside the drawer

high_descs: Walk forward until halfway to head of bed, turn right to face bed.
Pick up cell phone from bed.
Turn right, make a little left and right, cross room to dresser.
Put cell phone in middle drawer of dresser.
Walk to left side of dresser and face the clock.
Pick up cell phone from dresser.
Walk around dresser to face front of it.
Put cell phone in middle drawer to the right of other cell phone.
anns.task_desc: Put two cell phones in dresser drawer.

high_descs: Walk to the middle of the side of the bed in front of you and turn right.
Pick up the cell phone.
Turn right and walk until you're about three feet from the dresser then take a step or two left so you are almost past the dresser looking into the other room.
Open the third drawer from the top and put the phone in there.
Walk to the phone you see to the left of the light in front of you.
Pick up the phone.
Go back to where you put the first phone.
Put the phone next to the other one and close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Put two phones in the drawer.
